    <div class=" text-left">
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>1</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Supplemental Property Bill"]</strong> - @Localizer["Supplemental Property Bill"]
                @Localizer["to the Annual Secured Property Tax Bill and both must be paid by the date shown on the bill.  California State"]
                @Localizer["law requires the reassessment of property as of the first day of the month following an ownership change or the"]
                @Localizer["completion of new construction.  A change in ownership or a completion of new construction that occurs between"]
                @Localizer["January 1 and May 31 results in two supplemental assessments and triggers two Supplemental Property Tax Bills."]
                @Localizer["The first Supplemental Bill is for the remainder of the fiscal year in which the event occurred.  The second"]
                @Localizer["Supplemental Bill is for the subsequent fiscal year."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>2</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Assessor's Identification Number"]</strong> - @Localizer["This area identifies the Assessor’s Identification"]
                @Localizer["Number – (1234-567-890).  The Assessor’s Identification Number (AIN) is a ten-digit number assigned by the"]
                @Localizer["Office of the Assessor to each piece of real property in Los Angeles County.  This ten-digit AIN is made up of a"]
                @Localizer["four-digit Map Book Number (1234), a three-digit Page Number (567), and a three-digit Parcel Number (890)."]
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Year and Sequence"]</strong> - @Localizer["This area identifies the Year and Sequence – (16 000).  This five digit"]
                @Localizer["number is made up of a two-digit tax year and a three-digit sequence or bill type.  For example, a"]
                @Localizer["2016 annual bill is displayed as 16 000, however a 2016 supplemental bill may be displayed as 16 010."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>3</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Transfer/New Construction Date"]</strong> - @Localizer["This date is used as the basis for the change in"]
                @Localizer["assessed value.  The term \"Transfer Date\" refers to the recording date of an ownership change.  \"New Construction"]
                @Localizer["Date\" refers to the date the new construction was completed."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>4</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["General Tax Levy"]</strong> - @Localizer["This tax amount is the general one percent (1%) tax rate levied"]
                @Localizer["against every property in the County.  The calculation is 1 percent multiplied by the \"Net Taxable Value.\""]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>5</div>
            <p><strong>@Localizer["Voted Indebtedness"]</strong> - @Localizer["Voter-approved taxes levied against property."]</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>6</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Assessee"]</strong> - @Localizer["The owner of record and the mailing address on"]
                @Localizer["file with the Office of the Assessor."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>7</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Electronic Fund Transfer (EFT) Number"]</strong> - @Localizer["The EFT number is used to make"]
                @Localizer["credit card/Visa Debit card payments over the telephone.  To initiate a credit card/Visa Debit card payment,"]
                @Localizer["please call 1(888) 473-0835.  However, there are processing fees when paying by credit card/Visa Debit card."]
                @Localizer["Each transaction is limited to $99,999.99.  The PIN number is used to make electronic check payment to protect"]
                @Localizer["your security and privacy and is used to pay your current year and defaulted taxes online.  Effective with tax"]
                @Localizer["bills issued after August 2013, the PIN may contain all alpha, all numeric, or alpha/numeric characters."]
                @Localizer["The alpha letter 'O' is not used in the PIN.  The '0' is always a number zero."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>8</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Full Year Supplemental Taxes Due"]</strong> – @Localizer["The amount of taxes calculated for the entire"]
                @Localizer["fiscal year.  See Prorated Supplemental Taxes for the actual amount due."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>9</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Prorated Supplemental Taxes"]</strong> – @Localizer["The amount of total taxes due and payable for this"]
                @Localizer["bill.  See Field Number 12 for installment amounts and due dates."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>10</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Proration Factor"]</strong> - @Localizer["The mathematical factor used to prorate the amount of taxes"]
                @Localizer["due.  For more information, refer to the back of the bill."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>11</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Special Information"]</strong> - @Localizer["This section provides important information about the"]
                @Localizer["bill and states whether there are any delinquent taxes owed."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>12</div>
