                @Localizer["November 1 and is delinquent December 10.  If the first installment is not received or United States Postal Service"]
                @Localizer["(USPS) postmarked by December 10, a 10 percent penalty will be imposed.  The second installment is due February 1"]
                @Localizer["and is delinquent April 10.  If the second installment is not received or USPS postmarked on or before April 10,"]
                @Localizer["a 10 percent penalty and a $10.00 cost will be imposed.  Taxpayers must be sure to include the payment stub with"]
                @Localizer["any type of payment and write their Assessor's Identification Number with the Year/Sequence Number on their check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>13</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Property Location and/or Property Description"]</strong> - @Localizer["The property address and/or"]
