                @Localizer["Identification Number with the Year/Sequence Number on their check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>24</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Remit Amount"]</strong> - @Localizer["If payment is not made by the delinquency date, remit the amount"]
                @Localizer["stated here.  Include the payment stub(s) with the payment and write the Assessor’s Identification Number"]
                @Localizer["and the Year/Sequence Number on the check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>25</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Make Checks Payable"]</strong> - @Localizer["Make checks payable to the Los Angeles County Tax Collector"]
                @Localizer["and mail to this address.  Include the payment stub(s) with the payment and write the Assessor’s Identification"]
                @Localizer["Number and the Year/Sequence Number on the check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>26</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["1st Installment Delinquency Date"]</strong> - @Localizer["If paying the bill in full, payment"]
                @Localizer["must be received or United States Postal Service (USPS) postmarked by this date.  If paying in installments,"]
                @Localizer["the first installment must be received or USPS postmarked by this date, or a 10 percent penalty will be imposed."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>27</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["1st Installment Due"]</strong> - @Localizer["Amount of taxes due for the first installment."]
                @Localizer["Taxpayers must be sure to include the payment stub with any type of payment and write their Assessor’s"]
                @Localizer["Identification Number with the Year/Sequence Number on their check."]
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bill-step">
            <div>28</div>
            <p>
                <strong>@Localizer["Remit Amount"]</strong> - @Localizer["If payment is not made by the delinquency date, remit the amount"]
